FAQ.TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions
FAQ.Q1: How long does the evaluation take?
FAQ.A1: The complete evaluation of your skills usually takes between 2 to 4 weeks depending on the complexity of your file.
FAQ.A2: You must provide your diplomas, certificates, experience letters, and any document proving your professional skills.
FAQ.A3: The initial consultation is free. Accompaniment services are paid based on the level of support selected.
FAQ.Q4: In which languages do you offer services?
FAQ.A4: We offer our services in French, English, and several other languages depending on advisor availability.
